Purpose
This file declares the built-in agent set and turns it into a ready-to-use registry.

Linear intent
1. Build one list named `all` that contains the packaged built-in agents.
2. Keep that list explicit so the default system has a visible and auditable composition.
3. Create a new registry with a small initial capacity.
4. Register each built-in agent into that registry.
5. Return the registry so the rest of the system can run without extra wiring.

